      "content": "that's interesting. i like how you added the part about the cashier. could u expand on that? maybe describe how the character views the difference between their \"old world\" culture and the \"new world\" culture. like, maybe focus on how their culture is more about something specific—like being more emotional or traditional—versus how the westerners seem more cold or robotic?",
